 @* ----- Form Fields ----- *@
        <i data-lucide="heart" style="width:12px;height:12px;"></i> With Love <!-- Heart icon + label --> @* Renders part of the producers page markup. *@
    </div> @* Closes the matching HTML element. *@
 @* ----- Styling Section ----- *@
    <div class="gw-sticker gw-sticker--4" aria-hidden="true"> @* Starts a layout container for this section. *@
